\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Envelope theorem: behavioral changes don't have 1st-order effects on individual
 welfare.
 Only mechanical effects.
 But behavioral changes do have effect on government's budget â€“ the 
\emph on
Fiscal Externality.

